flowchart TD
  A[Customer approves page version] --> B[Deployment Agent preflight]
  B --> C{Release ready?}
  C -- Blocked --> D[Explain blockers]
  D --> E[Fix notes/routes/SEO/tracking]
  E --> B
  C -- Ready with warnings --> F[Show risk and recommendation]
  C -- Ready --> G[Create release plan]
  F --> H{Customer deploys?}
  G --> H
  H -- No --> I[Hold release or add notes]
  H -- Yes --> J[Queue Deploy Worker]
  J --> K[Netlify build and deploy]
  K --> L[Post-deploy verification]
  L --> M{Healthy?}
  M -- Yes --> N[Release report and monitoring]
  M -- No --> O[Rollback recommended]
  O --> P[Rollback Worker]
